@startuml
title IPsec / IKE Document Group Interrelationships (RFC 6071, Figure 1)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #FDEEEE
  BorderColor #B54A4A
}

[Architecture] as ARCH
[ESP Protocol] as ESP
[AH Protocol] as AH
[Encryption\nAlgorithm] as ENC
[Combined\nAlgorithm] as COMB
[Integrity-Protection\nAlgorithm] as INTEG
[IKE Protocol] as IKE

ARCH --> ESP
ARCH --> AH
ESP --> ENC
ESP --> COMB
ESP --> INTEG
AH --> INTEG
IKE --> ESP
IKE --> AH
IKE ..> ENC : negotiates
IKE ..> COMB : negotiates
IKE ..> INTEG : negotiates

note bottom of IKE
  IKE negotiates the SAs
  and keying material used
  by the protocol groups above.
end note
@enduml
